{"TopicId":149500,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"disabling other ground comms","CreatedByName":"rdem","CreatedById":125277,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-08T15:39:04Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"rdem","CreatedById":125277,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-08T15:39:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni think having only \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003Eksc\u003C/abbr\u003E as a control center makes the game way more fun. Geo sync comm network becomes meaningful\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheEpicSquared","CreatedById":158667,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-08T15:43:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can do this in the settings when starting a new game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"rdem","CreatedById":125277,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-08T15:54:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222793341\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149500\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475941393\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022158667\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TheEpicSquared\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 minutes ago, TheEpicSquared said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can do this in the settings when starting a new game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nnice! but it also should be in default hard mode.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"severedsolo","CreatedById":80345,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-08T18:29:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222793351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149500\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475942084\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022125277\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022rdem\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, rdem said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nnice! but it also should be in default hard mode.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt is.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"soulsource","CreatedById":110576,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-08T19:58:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDisclaimer: I haven\u0027t played 1.2 yet, my experience is based on Remote Tech.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA geostationary comm network isn\u0027t meaningful with a single control point either, as it\u0027s not a requirement to always have the same sat connect to \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E. You could just as well have a equilateral triangle of sats that can see each other at any altitude - one of them will always have line of sight to \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klesh","CreatedById":110814,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-08T20:07:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222793627\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149500\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475956738\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110576\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022soulsource\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, soulsource said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou could just as well have a equilateral triangle of sats that can see each other at any altitude - one of them will always have line of sight to \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThats what my testing playthrough looked like. \u00A0 I used 4, it worked fine with only \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E as a DSN.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jarin","CreatedById":71395,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-08T20:21:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe only\u00A0reason I like geostationary sats in RemoteTech is so that I\u0027ll always know where they are for antenna aiming purposes. Stock Comm doesn\u0027t care about that, so there\u0027s no point.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kelderek","CreatedById":131312,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-09T17:12:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222793627\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149500\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475956738\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110576\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022soulsource\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n21 hours ago, soulsource said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou could just as well have a equilateral triangle of sats that can see each other at any altitude - one of them will always have line of sight to \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, because of this you can choose an altitude that fits with the antenna ranges you want between Kerbin and elsewhere instead of needing to use the geostationary altitude\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xavven","CreatedById":100398,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-09T17:21:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222793516\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149500\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475951378\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002280345\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022severedsolo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 hours ago, severedsolo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt is.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHard mode player here... There are other ground stations enabled by default in Hard. The only difference is that they can\u0027t communicate over the horizon like in the easier modes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}